## mlld Directives (these lines should highlight)

@text greeting = "Hello, World!"  >> This is a comment
@data config = { "key": "value" }  << Another comment style
@run [echo "Running a command"]
@add @greeting
@path docs = [./docs]
@import { * } from "config.mld"
@exec build(target) = @run [npm run build -- @target]
@when any {
  @data.exists = @run [test -f data.json]
  @config.ready = true
}
@output [result.md]

## Reserved Variables

@text project = @.  >> @. is shorthand for @PROJECTPATH
@text input = @INPUT
@text timestamp = @TIME
@text root = @PROJECTPATH
@text stdin = @STDIN

